{
    "title": "Na Asa do Vento",
    "artist": "João do Vale e Luiz Vieira",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> \n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">(Passagem do E para A)</span>\n\n\n\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Deu meia noite, a lua faz um claro</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu assubo nos aro, vou brincar no vento leste</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A aranha tece puxando o fio da teia</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m\">C#m</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A ciência da abeia, da aranha e a minha</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Muita gente desconhece</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Muita gente desconhece, olalá, viu? </span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Muita gente desconhece</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Muita gente desconhece, olalá, tá?</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Muita gente desconhece</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A lua é clara, o sol tem rastro vermelho</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É o mar um grande espelho onde os dois vão se mirar</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#\">G#</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m\">C#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Rosa amarela quando murcha perde o cheiro</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#\">G#</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m\">C#m</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O amor é bandoleiro, pode inté custar dinheiro</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É fulô que não tem cheiro e todo mundo quer cheirar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Todo mundo quer cheirar, olalá, viu?</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Todo mundo quer cheirar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Todo mundo quer cheirar, olalá, tá?</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Todo mundo quer cheirar</span>\n",
